e2014.nat.gov.tw/en/TV/nm701000500000000.html |archive-date=2014-12-09 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n\n==Economy==\nThe township is home to the [[Hsinchu Industrial Park]].\n\n==Education==\n\n*[[China University of Technology]],Hsinchu campus\n*Hsinchu county Hukou senior high school, incl. grades 7 to 9\n*Hsinchu county Xinhu junior high school\n*Hsinchu county Chungcheng junior high school\n*Hsinchu county Hukou elementary school\n*Hsinchu county Changan elementary school\n*Hsinchu county Xinshih elementary school\n*Hsinchu county Xinhu elementary school\n*Hsinchu county Chungxing elementary school\n*Hsinchu county Hexing elementary school\n*Hsinchu county Huaxing elementary school\n\n{{Infobox Chinese\n| c = {{linktext|\u6e56\u53e3|\u9109}}\n| t = \u6e56\u53e3\u9109\n| s = \n| p = H\u00fak\u01d2u Xi\u0101ng\n| j = hu1 kou3 xiang1\n| mi = {{IPAc-cmn|h|u|2|.|k|ou|3|-|shi|ang|1}}\n| ci = \n| altname = [[Chinese name#Milk|Hukou Township]]\n| bpmf = \u310f\u3128\u02ca&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\u310e\u3121\u02c7&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\u3112\u3127\u3124\n| title = Hukou Township\n}}\n\n==Tourist attractions==\n* [[Armor School Museum]]\n*[[Hukou Old Street]]\n*Sanyuan Temple of Laohukou<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.hchcc.gov.tw/ch/06culture/cul_02_main.asp?bull_id=1067|title=Sanyuan Temple of Laohukou|last=|first=|date=|website=\u65b0\u7af9\u7e23\u6587\u5316\u5c40|access-date=}}</ref>\n*Catholic Church of Laohukou <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.hchcc.gov.tw/ch/06culture/cul_02_main.asp?bull_id=4166|title=Catholic Church of Laohukou|last=|first=|date=|website=\u65b0\u7af9\u7e23\u6587\u5316\u5c40|url-status=dead|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171027220536/http://www.hchcc.gov.tw/ch/06culture/cul_02_main.asp?bull_id=4166|archive-date=2017-10-27|access-date=}}</ref>[[File:Hukou Sanyuan Temple 20100731.jpg|thumb|Hukou Sanyuan Temple ]]<br />\n\n==Transportation==\n\n===Rail===\n[[File:TRA Hukou Station 2013.jpg|thumb|[[Hukou Station]]]]\nThe [[Taiwan Railways Administration]]