leas Kaimakli FC]] ||22||7||0||15||33||47||\u221214||'''14'''\n|-\n|10||align=left|[[AEK Ammochostos]] ||22||4||6||12||29||49||\u221220||'''14'''\n|-\n|11||align=left|[[Olimpiada Neapolis FC]] ||22||3||5||14||28||59||\u221231||'''11'''\n|- style=\"background: #FFCCCC;\"\n|12||align=left|[[ASOB Vatili]] ||22||0||1||21||12||108||\u221296||'''1'''||rowspan=1|Relegated to regional leagues\n|-\n|}\n\n<small>Points system: Won=2 points, Drawn=1 point, Lost=0 points</small>\n\n<small>Rules for classification: 1) Points, 2) Goal differences, 3) Goal for<br /></small>\n\n==Sources==\n*{{Cite news|title=\u03a4\u03b5\u03bb\u03b9\u03ba\u03ae \u03b2\u03b1\u03b8\u03bc\u03bf\u03bb\u03bf\u03b3\u03af\u03b1 \u03c4\u03b7\u03c2 \u0393\u0384 \u03ba\u03b1\u03c4\u03b7\u03b3\u03bf\u03c1\u03af\u03b1\u03c2 |page=2 |newspaper=[[Haravgi]] |date=1977-04-14|language=Greek}}\n*{{Cite journal|title=\u03a4\u03bf \u03c0\u03b5\u03c1\u03b9\u03bf\u03b4\u03b9\u03ba\u03cc \u03c4\u03b7\u03c2 \u039a\u039f\u03a0 |edition= |last=[[Cyprus Football Association]] |first= |publisher=[[Cyprus Football Association]] |location=\u039b\u03b5\u03c5\u03ba\u03c9\u03c3\u03af\u03b1 |date=February 2016 |issue=19 |isbn= |url=http://www.cfa.com.cy/images/DownloadsGr/KOP-T19%20FOR%20WEBSITE.pdf |pages=68\u201370 |ref=harv |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6fbwu9Pgh?url=http://www.cfa.com.cy/images/DownloadsGr/KOP-T19%20FOR%20WEBSITE.pdf |archivedate=2016-02-27 |language=Greek |url-status=dead |df= }}\n\n==See also==\n* [[Cypriot Third Division]]\n* [[1976\u201377 Cypriot First Division]]\n* [[1976\u201377 Cypriot Cup]]\n\n{{Cypriot Third Division}}\n{{1976\u201377 in Cypriot football}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:1976-77 Cypriot Third Division}}\n[[Category:Cypriot Third Division seasons]]\n[[Category:1976\u201377 in European third tier association football leagues|Cyprus]]\n[[Category:1976\u201377 in Cypriot football]]\n", "name_user": "Frietjes", "label": "safe", "comment": "expand templates perFb team TfD outcomeandFb competiti